==English==

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant}}

# To [[deprive]] of [[arms]]; to take away the [[weapon]]s of; to deprive of the means of [[attack]] or [[defense]]; to render [[defenseless]].
# To deprive of the means or the disposition to [[harm]]; to render [[harmless]] or [[innocuous]]; as, to disarm a man's wrath.

